HEADWORD: Befriend
<hw>Be*friend"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp.
& p. p.</pos> <conjf>Befriended</conjf>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
